metadata.name: POP Rocks by DNS_ERR
metadata.description:
POP Rocks is an ERC1155 token with a 10% supply and 1% mint price in contrast to the original Pop by CPG collection. 

By Poppers for Poppers: this token is for all CPG holders and new comers to gain insights into various tools and protocols.

Crypto Packaged Goods has been an extreme catalyst for change and inspiration in my journey through the web3 space thus drawing inspiration from CPG: Pop & Genesis Collection.

This Token will act as an access pass for future air drops from The Mad Scientist - DNS_ERR, potential artist and company collaborations, alpha access chats, charts & tools + the all important talent leveraging lifestyle all of which shall be finely curated over our diverse web of platforms including our notion site, telegram group & DNS_ERR personal twitter page.

We are cultivating our community in the coming days...  
More to come soon...  
Follow to stay up to date: https://twitter.com/DNS_ERR
